      <title>hexo搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/2021/07/02/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/"/>
      <url>/2021/07/02/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="hexo搭建个人博客-基于Windows-10"><a href="#hexo搭建个人博客-基于Windows-10" class="headerlink" title="hexo搭建个人博客(基于Windows 10)"></a>hexo搭建个人博客(基于Windows 10)</h1><h2 id="1-下载node"><a href="#1-下载node" class="headerlink" title="1.下载node"></a>1.下载node</h2><p>网址:<a href="https://nodejs.org/en/">https://nodejs.org/en/</a></p><p>傻瓜式安装</p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">node <span class="token operator">-</span>v     <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//查看node版本</span>npm  <span class="token operator">-</span>v     <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//查看npm版本</span></code></pre><h2 id="2-配置环境变量"><a href="#2-配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="2.配置环境变量"></a>2.配置环境变量</h2><h3 id="2-1-在高级系统设置中配置环境变量"><a href="#2-1-在高级系统设置中配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="2.1.在高级系统设置中配置环境变量"></a>2.1.在高级系统设置中配置环境变量</h3><p><img src="/2021/07/02/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/node%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F.png"></p><h3 id="2-2-把NODE-PATH添加在Path中"><a href="#2-2-把NODE-PATH添加在Path中" class="headerlink" title="2.2.把NODE_PATH添加在Path中"></a>2.2.把NODE_PATH添加在Path中</h3><h2 id="3-下载git"><a href="#3-下载git" class="headerlink" title="3.下载git"></a>3.下载git</h2><p>网址:<a href="https://git-scm.com/">https://git-scm.com/</a></p><p>傻瓜式安装</p><h3 id="3-1-在高级系统设置中-Path中配置环境变量"><a href="#3-1-在高级系统设置中-Path中配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="3.1.在高级系统设置中,Path中配置环境变量"></a>3.1.在高级系统设置中,Path中配置环境变量</h3><p>把下载的git路劲复制进去</p><pre class=" language-xml"><code class="language-xml">D:\Blogs\Git\Git\cmd;D:\Blogs\Git\Git\bin;D:\Blogs\Git\Git\mingw64\bin;D:\Blogs\Git\Git\mingw64\libexec\git-core;</code></pre><h2 id="4-打开命令行"><a href="#4-打开命令行" class="headerlink" title="4.打开命令行"></a>4.打开命令行</h2><h3 id="4-1-win-r输入cmd-回车"><a href="#4-1-win-r输入cmd-回车" class="headerlink" title="4.1 win+r输入cmd 回车"></a>4.1 win+r输入cmd 回车</h3><h3 id="4-2-安装淘宝的cnpm-管理器"><a href="#4-2-安装淘宝的cnpm-管理器" class="headerlink" title="4.2 安装淘宝的cnpm 管理器"></a>4.2 安装淘宝的cnpm 管理器</h3><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">输入 npm install <span class="token operator">-</span>g cnpm <span class="token operator">--</span>registry<span class="token operator">=</span>http<span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">/</span>registry<span class="token punctuation">.</span>npm<span class="token punctuation">.</span>taobao<span class="token punctuation">.</span>org    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">//cnpm -v    #查看cnpm版本</span></code></pre><h3 id="4-3-安装hexo框架"><a href="#4-3-安装hexo框架" class="headerlink" title="4.3 安装hexo框架"></a>4.3 安装hexo框架</h3><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">cnpm install <span class="token operator">-</span>g hexo<span class="token operator">-</span>cli    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// hexo -v    #查看hexo版本</span></code></pre><h3 id="4-4-选择一个盘-建立一个文件夹，在文件夹的路径下输入cmd回车"><a href="#4-4-选择一个盘-建立一个文件夹，在文件夹的路径下输入cmd回车" class="headerlink" title="4.4  选择一个盘 建立一个文件夹，在文件夹的路径下输入cmd回车"></a>4.4  选择一个盘 建立一个文件夹，在文件夹的路径下输入cmd回车</h3><h3 id="4-5生成博客-初始化博客"><a href="#4-5生成博客-初始化博客" class="headerlink" title="4.5生成博客 初始化博客"></a>4.5生成博客 初始化博客</h3><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">hexo init</code></pre><h3 id="4-6-打开博客"><a href="#4-6-打开博客" class="headerlink" title="4.6 打开博客"></a>4.6 打开博客</h3><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">hexo s</code></pre><p>在浏览器中输入localhost://4000 查看生成的博客</p><h2 id="5-进到github的官网"><a href="#5-进到github的官网" class="headerlink" title="5 进到github的官网"></a>5 进到github的官网</h2><h3 id="5-1-登录"><a href="#5-1-登录" class="headerlink" title="5.1 登录"></a>5.1 登录</h3><h3 id="5-2创建仓库"><a href="#5-2创建仓库" class="headerlink" title="5.2创建仓库"></a>5.2创建仓库</h3><p>  仓库起的名字一定要是  登录名称+.github.io。</p><p><strong>生成的仓库页面先不要关闭 一会要使用</strong></p><h3 id="5-3-安装一个插件"><a href="#5-3-安装一个插件" class="headerlink" title="5.3 安装一个插件"></a>5.3 安装一个插件</h3><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">cnpm install <span class="token operator">--</span>save hexo<span class="token operator">-</span>deployer<span class="token operator">-</span>git</code></pre><h2 id="6-设置配置文件"><a href="#6-设置配置文件" class="headerlink" title="6 设置配置文件"></a>6 设置配置文件</h2><p>在自己创建的文件下找到**_config.yml**文件，打开。</p><p>在最后找到</p><pre class=" language-javascript"><code class="language-javascript">deploy<span class="token punctuation">:</span>  type<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token string">'git'</span>  repo<span class="token punctuation">:</span>  找到生成仓库的页面 把 SSH 后面的路劲复制到repo后面    branch<span class="token punctuation">:</span>  master</code></pre><p> <strong>冒号： 后面一定要跟空格</strong></p><h2 id="7-把博客发布到github上"><a href="#7-把博客发布到github上" class="headerlink" title="7 把博客发布到github上"></a>7 把博客发布到github上</h2><p> 在生成的文件夹下鼠标右键</p><p><img src="/2021/07/02/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%A1%8C.png"></p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">输入 hexo d</code></pre><h2 id="8-配置过程中遇见的问题"><a href="#8-配置过程中遇见的问题" class="headerlink" title="8 配置过程中遇见的问题"></a>8 配置过程中遇见的问题</h2><h3 id="8-1-hexo-d-出错"><a href="#8-1-hexo-d-出错" class="headerlink" title="8.1 hexo  d 出错"></a>8.1 hexo  d 出错</h3><p> 报错原因：<strong>ERROR Deployer not found: git</strong></p><p>解决办法：这是因为没安装<code>hexo-deployer-git</code>插件，在命令行中输入</p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">cnpm install hexo<span class="token operator">-</span>deployer<span class="token operator">-</span>git <span class="token operator">--</span>savegit config <span class="token operator">--</span>global user<span class="token punctuation">.</span>name  IT<span class="token operator">-</span>FeiZai <span class="token string">"yourname"</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>注册时的账号<span class="token punctuation">)</span>git config <span class="token operator">--</span>global user<span class="token punctuation">.</span>email  <span class="token number">2742252980</span><span class="token annotation punctuation">@qq</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>com<span class="token string">"youremail"</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>注册时的邮箱<span class="token punctuation">)</span>     然后再hexo  d   </code></pre><h3 id="8-2-hexo-init-出错"><a href="#8-2-hexo-init-出错" class="headerlink" title="8.2 hexo  init 出错"></a>8.2 hexo  init 出错</h3><p>查看上面的变量是否配置完全</p><h3 id="8-3-hexo-d-出错"><a href="#8-3-hexo-d-出错" class="headerlink" title="8.3 hexo  d 出错"></a>8.3 hexo  d 出错</h3><p>报错原因：OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection was reset, errno 10054</p><p>解决办法： 打开命令行，输入</p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">git config <span class="token operator">--</span>global http<span class="token punctuation">.</span>sslVerify <span class="token string">"false"</span>然后再执行hexo  d</code></pre><h3 id="8-4-hexo-d-连接超时"><a href="#8-4-hexo-d-连接超时" class="headerlink" title="8.4 hexo d  连接超时"></a>8.4 hexo d  连接超时</h3><p><img src="/2021/07/02/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E8%B6%85%E6%97%B6.png"></p><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java"> 先执行  git config <span class="token operator">--</span>global <span class="token operator">--</span>unset http<span class="token punctuation">.</span>proxy 在执行  hexo d  或者是网络不好 更会再执行 hexo  d </code></pre><h2 id="9-常用命令"><a href="#9-常用命令" class="headerlink" title="9 常用命令"></a>9 常用命令</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">hexo  clean  清理hexo    g  生成hexo    d   发布    hexo    s  查看本地博客     npm outdated  查看安装插件的版本</code></pre><h2 id="10-安装插件"><a href="#10-安装插件" class="headerlink" title="10 安装插件"></a>10 安装插件</h2><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">安装软件 用cnpm   不要用npm<span class="token operator">!</span><span class="token operator">!</span><span class="token operator">!</span>  </code></pre><h3 id="10-1-图片插件"><a href="#10-1-图片插件" class="headerlink" title="10.1 图片插件"></a>10.1 图片插件</h3><pre class=" language-java"><code class="language-java">使用 cnpm install https<span class="token operator">:</span><span class="token operator">/</span><span class="token operator">/</span>github<span class="token punctuation">.</span>com<span class="token operator">/</span>CodeFalling<span class="token operator">/</span>hexo<span class="token operator">-</span>asset<span class="token operator">-</span>image <span class="token operator">--</span>save 不要使用 cnpm install hexo<span class="token operator">-</span>asset<span class="token operator">-</span>image <span class="token operator">--</span>save这个命令安装<span class="token punctuation">,</span>版本号不对</code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
